# Taker Protocol Light Mining Bot

This project automates registration, Twitter binding, and periodic mining tasks for Taker Light Mining.

## Key Components
- [main.py](mdc:main.py) - Main entry point with interactive CLI menu
- [config.py](mdc:config.py) - Core configuration settings
- [settings.yaml](mdc:settings.yaml) - User-configurable overrides
- [utils/](mdc:utils/) - Helper modules and utilities
- [tasks/](mdc:tasks/) - Task-specific implementation modules
- `data/` - Input files directory (private keys, proxies, etc.)
- `results/` - Output files directory for task results
- [taker.db](mdc:taker.db) - SQLite database for account data storage
